  <answerContent><![CDATA[<h3>Post-holiday issues</h3>
<p>If you have returned from your holiday and would like to get in touch with our Guest Relations team or make a complaint, please do so by writing to us by email or via post. If you prefer, you can also complete our customer contact form below and we will endeavour to reply to your enquiry as soon as possible.</p>
<p>In order for us to deal with your queries, please provide as much information as possible, including your booking reference and holiday dates.</p>
<p><strong>By email: </strong><a href="mailto:guest.services@inghams.co.uk">guest.relations@inghams.co.uk</a></p>
<p><strong>By post:</strong></p>
<p>Guest Services<br />Inghams<br />Nelson House<br />55 Victoria Road<br />Farnborough<br />Hampshire<br />GU14 7PA</p>
<h3>Lost Property</h3>
<p>If you need to get in touch about an item of lost property, please get in touch with our overseas team in your destination using one of the following email addresses:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="mailto:lostpropertyANDORRA@inghams.co.uk">lostpropertyANDORRA@inghams.co.uk</a></li>
